<br />

<br />
Magicians are able to solo some impressive things, not old world content that you claim.  Check out some of the posts on this board for some of the accomplishments.  Solo'ing for experience isn't tough nowadays either.  It's not as efficient as grouping, but then again, it shouldn't be. 
<br />

